{"tid":1847954,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭：為避造成誘因決定向非本地居民收取醫藥費","createTime":"2020-01-28T09:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T11:17:38.000Z","uid":20933,"like":122,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"5bbc0ca9f896e735147b61817a7b2bca6ef68886","tid":1847954,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:07:33.000Z","msg":"醫管局日前指，非本地居民到公立醫院接受新型肺炎治療，會獲豁免收費。行政長官林鄭月娥指，留意到社會相當關注相關情況，決定因時制宜，向所有非本地居民收費，以免造成誘因, 增加本地醫療系統的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，根據公共衛生政策，患有法定呈報傳染病的病人會被豁免醫療費用，是為了避免病人因考慮醫療費用而迴避治療，政策沿用多年，但今次考慮到要因時制宜，調整做法。"},{"pid":"cfd7a27e7526a6231363608fa7d5381c0e12121b","tid":1847954,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:07:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1256611&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1256611%26csid%3D261_341&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb1e0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=5156257b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1256611&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"2f3b41806a0d2e2ad6d4c5217d2a10fa03175616","tid":1847954,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:08:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">匿埋喺屋企出唔到街？<br />\n唔夠口罩唔敢出去？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Twitter 戰線永遠需要你！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">入去 <a href=\"http://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb1e0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=c9d52e08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a> 撳 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">/task2</span></span> 拎任務</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Retweet + Like + Reply</span></span><br />\nTask 2 好缺人，大家快啲去幫手！<br />\n<span style=\"colo